Package aom.scripting.xs.rm

Enum Terrain

Object
Enum<Terrain>
Terrain
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Terrain>, Constable
public enum Terrain
extends Enum<Terrain>
This is an enumeration of all terrain types. For the correct spelling please refer to the documentation rather than the variables.
Author:
Mythic_Freak - mythic.freak[a]gmail.com
Note
There's a pretty cool download at AoMH called EPIC Terrains that update all existing terrains with more detailed versions. Check it out here. It also contains unit texture upgrades currently, you might want to skip those.
